      "sourceEvidence": ["utils/directoryTreeCache.ts", "components/FolderTree.svelte"],
      "targetContract": "单层列举使用原生 opendir/Dirent；递归索引与搜索使用唯一 readdirp adapter，支持 AbortSignal、背压和批次输出。",
      "surfaces": ["GUI", "CLI", "TUI"],
      "status": "partial",
      "testIds": ["neoview.file-tree.opendir", "neoview.file-tree.readdirp", "neoview.file-tree.scan-limit", "neoview.folder.file-tree-service"],
      "notes": "单层 opendir provider 与 readdirp scanner 已由 ReaderFileTreeService 按 session 根统一编排；流式 HTTP 搜索 surface 与排除规则仍待完成。"
    },
    {
      "id": "folder.arch.watch",
      "category": "architecture",
      "title": "文件树增量监听",
      "sourceEvidence": ["utils/directoryTreeCache.ts", "components/FolderTree.svelte"],
      "targetContract": "按需动态加载 @parcel/watcher，仅监听活动根；事件合并后增量修补 generation，最后消费者关闭即 unsubscribe。",
      "surfaces": ["GUI", "CLI", "TUI"],
      "status": "partial",
      "testIds": ["neoview.file-tree.watcher", "neoview.file-tree.watcher-native", "neoview.folder.file-tree-service", "neoview.folder.watch-http", "neoview.folder.watch-cancellation"],
      "notes": "watch:true 显式 session 已接入目录快照失效、单飞重读、generation 递增、导航换根和关闭 unsubscribe；前端默认 opt-in、事件推送/轮询和增量行补丁仍待完成。"
    },
    {
